FBIS4-47723 "drafr085_a_94003" FBIS-AFR-94-085 Daily Report 2 May 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Rwanda Radio Mille Collines Says Tutsi Massacres To End Radio Mille Collines Says Tutsi Massacres To End LD0205153794 Brussels La Une Radio Network in French 1500 GMT 2 May 94 LD0205153794 Brussels La Une Radio Network French BFN [Excerpts] The announcer of Radio Mille Collines, in Rwanda, has denied the allegations against him. [passage omitted] Moreover, according to the international human rights organization, Human Rights, Radio Mille Collines has announced that the extermination of Tutsis and Hutu opponents in Rwanda will end on Thursday 5 May, when President Habyarimana will be buried.
